<collectingCountry id="F31CBCD0FF91BD47FDDAFE588B80FE2B" box="[582,642,424,446]" name="Nepal" pageId="6" pageNumber="1555">Nepal</collectingCountry>
in the east (
<bibRefCitation id="EF9A81B1FF91BD47FC9AFE588A9CFE2B" author="ASSING V" box="[774,926,424,446]" journalOrPublisher="Beitrage zur Entomologie, Keltern" pageId="6" pageNumber="1555" pagination="89 - 148" part="61" refId="ref3466" refString="ASSING V. (2011 a): A revision of the genus Neosclerus CAMERON (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae). - Beitrage zur Entomologie, Keltern 61 (1): 89 - 148." title="A revision of the genus Neosclerus CAMERON (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Paederinae)" type="journal article" year="2011">ASSING 2011a</bibRefCitation>
